original_font_information.description: Maison Neue is the thoroughly reworked version of our early Maison typeface family. While the original version was constructed on geometric principles, Maison Neue has now been meticulously redrawn and extended. Paying particular attention to harmony, rhythm and flow, the new typeface also accounts for up-to-date display and reproduction technologies to create a distinctly contemporary grotesque, with a classic touch. The whole family contains 40 styles thus far; each includes an extended Latin character set and a variety of OpenType features.
